\[P(2\leq X\leq 4) =p(2)+p(3)+p(4)\] \[=[p(0)+\cdots+p(4)]-[p(0)+p(1)]\] \[=P(X\leq 4)-P\big{(}X\leq 1\big{)}\] \[=F(4)-F\big{(}1\big{)}\]

