## Proposition

Let \(X\) have a gamma distribution with parameters \(\alpha\) and \(\beta\). Then for any \(x>0\), the cdf of \(X\) is given by

\[P(X\leq x)=G\left(\frac{x}{\beta};\alpha\right),\]

