\[S_{XX}(f) = \mathcal{T}\{R_{XX}(\tau)\}=\mathcal{T}\big{\{}250+1500\text{exp} \big{(}1.6\times 10^{9}\tau^{2}\big{)}\big{\}}\] \[= 2508(f)+1500\mathcal{T}\big{\{}\text{exp}\big{(}-1.6\times 10^{9} \tau^{2}\big{)}\big{\}}\]

